OL,3,CDaniel Dubois plots long reign as
OL,4,Cworld heavyweight champion
OL,6,FDaniel Dubois is plotting a long reign
OL,7,Fas world heavyweight champion after
OL,8,Fdemonstrating his mental toughness in
OL,9,Fa gripping firefight win over British
OL,10,Frival Fabio Wardley.
OL,12,FPut on to the seat of his pants after
OL,13,Fjust 10 seconds, Dubois also took a
OL,14,Fknee in the third round after another
OL,15,Fbrutal overhand right from Wardley,
OL,16,Fwho was making the first defence of
OL,17,Fhis WBO title.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
