OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778461395
OL,3,CDaniel Dubois plots long reign as
OL,4,Cworld heavyweight champion
OL,6,FBut Dubois, whose ability to dig deep
OL,7,Fwhen he is in the trenches has been
OL,8,Fquestioned in the past, reversed the
OL,9,Ftide and left Wardley a crimson mess
OL,10,Fto earn an 11th-round stoppage in
OL,11,FManchester.
OL,13,FA rematch clause is in place and
OL,14,FDubois, a former WBA 'regular' and IBF
OL,15,Fchampion admitted he was happy to go
OL,16,Fagain, after proving his fortitude in
OL,17,Fa thunderous war for the ages at the
OL,18,FCo-op Live.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
