OL,3,CDaniel Dubois plots long reign as
OL,4,Cworld heavyweight champion
OL,6,F"I'm going to go on another good run `
OL,7,FI need a nice rest now," said Dubois,
OL,8,Fwho said he took more satisfaction
OL,9,Ffrom this win than what he did from
OL,10,Fbeating Anthony Joshua in September
OL,11,F2024.
OL,13,F"I was a bit nervy to start off with
OL,14,Fand a bit all over the place but I
OL,15,Fpulled it together and got the victory.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@XO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
