PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778461395
OL,3,CDaniel Dubois plots long reign as
OL,4,Cworld heavyweight champion
OL,6,F"I needed to get whacked, come back
OL,7,Fup, I felt like a warrior in there,
OL,8,Fdigging deep and coming back. I wasn't
OL,9,Fgoing to be denied. I owed my dad and
OL,10,Fthe people in my corner and I couldn't
OL,11,Flet them down.
OL,13,F"I want to congratulate Fabio on a
OL,14,Fgreat fight. What a warrior he is,
OL,15,Fhe's a tough cookie. He took my shots
OL,16,Fand just tested me. If the rematch
OL,17,Fhappens, bring it on."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
