OL,3,CDaniel Dubois plots long reign as
OL,4,Cworld heavyweight champion
OL,6,FDubois was ridiculed and labelled a
OL,7,F"quitter" by fellow boxers after
OL,8,Flosing for the first time to Joe Joyce
OL,9,Fin 2020, while a couple of stoppage
OL,10,Fdefeats to Oleksandr Usyk put more
OL,11,Fscrutiny on the Londoner.
OL,13,FAfter being poleaxed by the Ukrainian
OL,14,Flast July, footage emerged of Dubois
OL,15,Fand his father hosting a party at
OL,16,Ftheir household just hours beforehand,
OL,17,Falthough they did the same ahead of
OL,18,Fhis win over Joshua.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
