OL,3,CDaniel Dubois plots long reign as
OL,4,Cworld heavyweight champion
OL,6,FDubois (23-3 22KOs) was pensive before
OL,7,Ffacing Wardley, walking out of two
OL,8,Finterviews, but trainer Don Charles `
OL,9,Ffired then rehired after the second
OL,10,FUsyk defeat ` believes his charge has
OL,11,Fsilenced his critics.
OL,13,F"No human being on this planet could
OL,14,Fever question this kid ever again,"
OL,15,FCharles said. "Certainly don't
OL,16,Fquestion him in front of me. What he
OL,17,Fshowed, he erased any doubt of all the
OL,18,Fnegative talk.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@cO]wD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
