OL,3,CDaniel Dubois plots long reign as
OL,4,Cworld heavyweight champion
OL,6,F"Because we were victorious, it's
OL,7,Falmost like I'm glad the fight went
OL,8,Fthat way so he could demonstrate, this
OL,9,Fquitting narrative is not right. I
OL,10,Fthink he ticked every box."
