OL,3,CDaniel Dubois plots long reign as
OL,4,Cworld heavyweight champion
OL,6,FWardley's fairytale run from boxing on
OL,7,Fwhite-collar shows to becoming world
OL,8,Fchampion was built on his resilience,
OL,9,Ftwice coming back from the brink to
OL,10,Fstop Justis Huni and Joseph Parker in
OL,11,Fthe last 12 months.
OL,13,FBut the bridge of his nose was gushing
OL,14,Fblood and his right eye was almost
OL,15,Fswollen shut before referee Howard
OL,16,FFoster stepped in as Wardley suffered
OL,17,Fthe first defeat of his 22-fight
OL,18,Fprofessional career.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
