OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778461395
OL,3,CDaniel Dubois plots long reign as
OL,4,Cworld heavyweight champion
OL,6,FThe punishment Wardley sustained led
OL,7,Fto accusations his team or Foster
OL,8,Fcould have interjected earlier, with
OL,9,Fthe Ipswich fighter twice inspected by
OL,10,Fthe ringside doctor ahead of the ninth
OL,11,Fand 10th rounds.
OL,13,FBut Frank Warren, who promotes both
OL,14,FWardley and Dubois, said: "There's
OL,15,Fnothing to complain about with this
OL,16,Ffight, it was a great fight."
OL,26,@vD@[OUxD@]O]
